          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When the peaceful continent of Tasos is invaded by the evil minions which belong to the four titans who threaten to break free from their seals, you know you're going to need some hero companions by your side. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Rogue Heroes: Ruins of Tasos",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a four-player co-op roguelite adventure, with topdown action gameplay that screams nostalgia. Explore the land of Tasos, solve puzzles in the depths of menacing dungeons and share the glory alongside friends.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
